<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Pawz</title>
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="~/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
</head>
<body>

    <!-- About Us Section -->
    <section class="about-us-section py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center">About Pawz</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                    <p>Pawz is dedicated to enhancing the lives of pets and their owners. Our mission is to provide a safe, friendly, and reliable platform where you can find your next furry friend, whether through adoption or purchase. We believe every pet deserves a loving home, and every pet owner deserves a happy companion.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h3>Why Choose Pawz?</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Extensive Selection:</strong> From adorable puppies and kittens to exotic pets, we offer a wide range of animals to suit any preference.</li>
                        <li><strong>Trusted Platform:</strong> Our platform connects you with verified breeders and shelters to ensure the well-being of every pet.</li>
                        <li><strong>Commitment to Adoption:</strong> We are passionate about helping pets find their forever homes and support various adoption initiatives.</li>
                        <li><strong>Comprehensive Support:</strong> Our team is here to provide guidance and support throughout your journey of finding the perfect pet.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row mt-4">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <h3>Meet Our Pets</h3>
                    <p>At Pawz, you can meet a diverse range of pets, each with its unique personality. Our platform allows you to view detailed profiles of each pet, including their needs and characteristics, to help you make an informed decision. Whether you're looking for a playful puppy, a cuddly kitten, or an exotic pet, we have something for everyone.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer py-4 bg-light">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Pawz | <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="#">Terms of Use</a></p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>

